# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok minis will return to the world rally championship starting next year , german automaker bmw announced tuesday .
# ::alignments
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "BMW")
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Germany"))
            :ARG0-of (m / make-01
                  :ARG1 (a2 / automobile)))
      :ARG1 (r / return-01
            :ARG1 (p / person
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Minis"))
            :ARG4 (c3 / championship
                  :mod (r2 / rally-01)
                  :mod (w / world))
            :ARG1-of (s / start-01
                  :time (y / year
                        :mod (n4 / next))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok former indonesian dictator suharto can now walk unaided , but is still too ill to stand trial on multimillion dollar corruption charges , one of his lawyers said sunday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :quant 1
            :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Suharto")
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Indonesia"))
                              :ARG2 (d / dictator)
                              :time (f / former)))
                  :ARG2 (l / lawyer)))
      :ARG1 (c2 / contrast-01
            :ARG1 (p3 / possible-01
                  :ARG1 (w / walk-01
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :manner (b / blind-02
                              :ARG1 p2))
                  :time (n3 / now))
            :ARG2 (h3 / have-degree-91
                  :ARG1 p2
                  :ARG2 (ii / ill-01
                        :ARG1 p2)
                  :ARG3 (t / too)
                  :ARG6 (s2 / stand-03
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (t2 / try-02
                              :ARG1 p2
                              :ARG2 (c3 / charge-05
                                    :ARG1 p2
                                    :ARG2 (c4 / corrupt-01
                                          :ARG1 (m / multiple
                                                :op1 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                                                      :quant 1000000000
                                                      :unit (d2 / dollar)))))))
                  :mod (s3 / still)))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (s4 / sunday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the united states maintained trade sanctions against ukraine worth ## million dollars -lrb- ## million euros -rrb- on wednesday for its failure to crack down on cd piracy despite new measures to combat the trade .
# ::alignments
(m / maintain-01
      :ARG0 (s / state
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "United"
                  :op2 "States"))
      :ARG1 (s2 / sanction-02
            :ARG0 s
            :ARG1 (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Ukraine"))
            :mod (t / trade-01)
            :ARG1-of (w / worth-01
                  :ARG2 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                        :quant 1000000
                        :unit (d / dollar))))
      :time (w2 / wednesday)
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (f / fail-01
                  :ARG1 c
                  :ARG2 (c3 / crack-down-06
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG1 (p / piracy
                              :mod (p2 / product
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "CD"))))
                  :concession (m3 / measure-02
                        :ARG1 (c4 / combat-01
                              :ARG1 p)
                        :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01)))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok malaysia 's leader was expected to retain power easily as voting began sunday in an election that will also decide how strong the fundamentalist islamic opposition will be in this mostly muslim country .
# ::alignments
(e / expect-01
      :ARG1 (r / retain-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Malaysia"))))
            :ARG1 (p2 / power)
            :ARG1-of (e2 / easy-05))
      :time (b / begin-01
            :ARG1 (v / vote-01
                  :subevent-of (e3 / elect-01
                        :ARG0-of (d / decide-01
                              :ARG1 (t / thing
                                    :degree-of (s / strong-02
                                          :ARG1 (o / oppose-01
                                                :ARG0 (f / fundamentalist
                                                      :mod (r2 / religious-group
                                                            :name (n2 / name
                                                                  :op1 "Islam")))
                                                :location (c2 / country
                                                      :mod r2
                                                      :name (n3 / name
                                                            :op1 "Islam"))
                                                :mod (m / most)))))
                        :mod (a / also)))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / sunday))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok max mirnyi made a quick work of lucas arnold #-# , #-# in the reverse singles in minsk on sunday to extend belarus ' lead over argentina to #-# in their davis cup world group quarterfinal .
# ::alignments
(w / work-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Max"
                  :op2 "Mirnyi"))
      :ARG1 (e / extend-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (l / lead-02
                  :ARG0 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Belarus"))
                  :ARG2 (c2 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Argentina")))
            :ARG4 (c3 / country
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Denmark"))
            :ARG5 (c4 / country
                  :name (n5 / name
                        :op1 "South"
                        :op2 "America"))
            :time (f / final
                  :subevent-of (g / group
                        :name (n6 / name
                              :op1 "Davis"
                              :op2 "Cup")
                        :mod (w2 / world))))
      :ARG1-of (q / quick-02)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s / sunday)))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok president george w. bush pleaded with north korean leader kim jong il in a letter to keep his promise to fully disclose all nuclear programs by year 's end , in the most personal bush diplomatic approach toward pyongyang since he called the country part of the `` axis of evil .
# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (p2 / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "George"
                  :op2 "W."
                  :op3 "Bush")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (p3 / president)))
      :ARG1 (p4 / person
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Kim"
                  :op2 "Jong"
                  :op3 "Il")
            :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "North"
                              :op2 "Korea"))))
      :ARG2 (k / keep-02
            :ARG0 p4
            :ARG1 (p5 / promise-01
                  :ARG0 p4
                  :ARG1 (d / disclose-01
                        :ARG0 p4
                        :ARG1 (p6 / program
                              :mod (n4 / nucleus)
                              :mod (a / all))
                        :degree (f / full)
                        :time (b / by
                              :op1 (e / end-01
                                    :ARG1 (y / year))))))
      :medium (l2 / letter)
      :manner (a2 / approach-02
            :ARG0 p2
            :ARG1 (c2 / city
                  :name (n5 / name
                        :op1 "Pyongyang"))
            :manner (d2 / diplomacy)
            :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (p7 / personal-02
                        :ARG1 a2)
                  :ARG3 (m / most))
            :time (s / since
                  :op1 (c3 / call-01
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (c4 / country)
                        :ARG2 (p8 / part
                              :part-of (a3 / axis
                                    :mod (e2 / evil)))))))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG1 (s / share
            :mod (c2 / continent
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Europe")))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (w / wednesday))
      :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (h / help-01
                  :ARG0 (s2 / strong-02
                        :ARG1 (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (p2 / produce-01
                                    :ARG1 (o / oil))))
                  :ARG1 (o2 / offset-01
                        :ARG0 s2
                        :ARG1 (w2 / worry-01
                              :ARG0 (r / rate
                                    :mod (ii / interest))
                              :ARG1 (p3 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (ii2 / invest-01)))))
            :mod (m / most)))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok with drought in the air and wildfires possible into the fall , joe <unk> believes he may have a better market this year .
# ::alignments
(b / believe-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Joe"
                  :op2 "Illustration"))
      :ARG1 (p2 / possible-01
            :ARG1 (h / have-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (m / market
                        :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (g / good-02
                                    :ARG1 m)
                              :ARG3 (m2 / more)))
                  :time (y / year
                        :mod (t / this))))
      :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
            :ARG0 (a / and
                  :op1 (d / drought
                        :location (a2 / air))
                  :op2 (w / wildfire
                        :ARG1-of (p3 / possible-01
                              :time (d2 / date-entity
                                    :season (f / fall)))))))

# ::id 8 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok two israelis were shot and injured in a palestinian <unk> shooting attack monday morning near tel aviv , israel radio reported .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (r2 / radio
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Israel")))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (s / shoot-02
                  :ARG1 (p / person
                        :quant 2
                        :mod c))
            :op2 (ii / injure-01
                  :ARG1 p)
            :subevent-of (a2 / attack-01
                  :ARG1 (s2 / shoot-02)
                  :location (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Palestine"))
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (m / monday)
                        :dayperiod (m2 / morning))
                  :ARG1-of (n3 / near-02
                        :ARG2 (c3 / city
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Tel"
                                    :op2 "Aviv"))))))

                              :poss p3)))))

# ::id 10 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok as facebook has blossomed into a hot internet hangout , its users have passed countless hours playing scrabble with friends -- or at least , an <unk> unauthorized version of the word game that scrabble 's owners have tried to shut down .
# ::alignments
(p / pass-03
      :ARG0 (p2 / person
            :ARG0-of (u / use-01
                  :ARG1 (p3 / publication
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Facebook"))))
      :ARG1 (c / countless
            :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (h / hour)))
      :ARG2 (p4 / play-01
            :ARG0 p2
            :ARG1 (g / game
                  :name n
                  :op1 "Scrabble")
            :mod (v / version
                  :ARG1-of (a / authorize-01
                        :polarity -)
                  :mod (w / word)
                  :ARG1-of (s / shut-down-05
                        :ARG0 (p5 / person
                              :ARG0-of (o / own-01
                                    :ARG1 g))
                        :ARG1-of (t2 / try-01
                              :ARG0 p5))))
      :accompanier (p6 / person
            :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                  :ARG1 g
                  :ARG2 (f / friend)))
      :time (b / blossom-01
            :ARG1 p3
            :ARG4 (h3 / hangout
                  :location (ii / internet)
                  :ARG1-of (h4 / hot-05))))

            :ARG0 (s2 / stabilize-01

                        :ARG1 m

                                    :ARG2 (l3 / low-04
                                          :ARG1 l2)

                                          :op1 (m4 / march-01))))
                        :time (d2 / date-entity
                              :weekday (m5 / monday))))))

                  :op2 "Inc.")

                  :mod (s / service)))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (c2 / cut-02
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (j / job
                        :mod (a2 / additional)))
            :op2 (r / reduce-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (s2 / size
                        :poss (s3 / store)))
            :op3 (d / discontinue-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (l / line
                        :mod (p2 / product)
                        :quant (s4 / some)))
            :subevent-of (p3 / plan-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (r2 / reorganize-01
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG1 (b / bankrupt-01))
                  :ARG1-of (g / go-on-15))))

# ::id 21 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (a / authority)
      :ARG1 (a2 / attack-01
            :ARG0 (g / gangster
                  :quant 10
                  :ARG1-of (a3 / arm-01))
            :ARG1 (v / village
                  :location (w / west
                        :part-of (c2 / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Kenya"))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday)
                  :dayperiod (n2 / night))
            :manner (a4 / and
                  :op1 (k / kill-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (p / person
                              :quant (a5 / at-least
                                    :op1 100)))
                  :op2 (ii / injure-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :quant 12
